headline: WEC Energy Group to announce 2025 second-quarter results July 30
summary: WEC Energy Group Inc. (NYSE: WEC) will issue its 2025 second-quarter earnings news release before the stock market opens Wednesday, July 30. A conference call for investors and security analysts is scheduled for the same day at 1 p.m. Central time.
